metadata.name: New Frontier
metadata.description:
At the cutting edge, right at the border between our world and the unknown, that's where creation burns:

The fire that converts potential into reality.

It is never safe but always teaching.
Never new but always fresh. 
Never repeating but always crashing like a wave.

It lives in the only moment anything ever lives in:
right here and right now.

---
Rick Vito, 2020-2022
StyleGan2-ADA, StableDiffusion, Digital paint
